### [1 Chronicles Chapter 18](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#001.md)

[1 Chronicles](../../../bib/kjv/ch1001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ch1 18:0</span></span>

David's victories.

[1 Chronicles 18:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_001">ch1 18:1</span></span>

This chapter is the same as 2 Samuel 8. Our good fight of faith, under
the Captain of our salvation, will end in everlasting triumph and peace.
The happiness of Israel, through David's victories, and just government,
faintly shadowed forth the happiness of the redeemed in the realms
above.

